I"Ç<h2 id="steps">Steps</h2>
<p>You can create a new simple(nodejs + express) app and deploy to azure:</p>

<h3 id="step-1">Step 1</h3>
<p>install express
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">npm install express-generator -g</code></p>

<h3 id="step-2">Step 2</h3>

<p>create an express sample application:
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">express newappname</code></p>

<h3 id="step-3">Step 3</h3>

<p>cd newappname
   change directory:
     <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&gt; cd newapp</code></p>

<p>install dependencies:
     <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&gt; npm install</code></p>

<p>run the app locally:
     <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&gt; SET DEBUG=newapp:* &amp; npm start</code></p>
<h3 id="step-4">Step 4</h3>
<p>git init &amp;  Azure deployment center - CI/CD 
   choose local git or github</p>

<h3 id="step-5">Step 5</h3>
<p>in vs code - azure app service
   deploy to related app</p>

